{"LIZA":[{"def":"The American white mullet (Mugil curema).","pos":""}],"LIZARD":[{"def":"Any one of the numerous species of reptiles belonging to the order Lacertilia; sometimes, also applied to reptiles of other orders, as the Hatteria.","pos":""},{"def":"A piece of rope with thimble or block spliced into one or both of the ends.","pos":""}],"LIZARD'S TAIL":[{"def":"A perennial plant of the genus Saururus (S.","pos":""}]}